description: Erection of two buildings (4-storeys and 6-storeys) to provide 73 (36 private and 37 affordable) residential units (7 x 4-bedroom, 9 x 3-bedroom, 20 x 2-bedroom, and 37 x 1-bedroom) with 30 car parking spaces (20 underground and 10 surface level), 93 cycle parking spaces, and associated landscaping (following demolition of all existing buildings on site).
